---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="关于" bodyClass="about-page">
  <div class="page-header page-header--about">
    <h1 class="page-title">关于</h1>
    <span class="page-subtitle">博客简介页（示例）</span>
    <div class="page-actions">
      <a
        class="icon-link"
        href="https://github.com/cxro/astro-whono"
        aria-label="GitHub"
        title="GitHub"
      >
        <svg class="icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false">
          <path
            d="M12 2c-5.5 0-10 4.6-10 10.2 0 4.5 2.9 8.3 6.9 9.7.5.1.7-.2.7-.5v-1.9c-2.8.6-3.4-1.2-3.4-1.2-.5-1.2-1.1-1.5-1.1-1.5-.9-.6.1-.6.1-.6 1 .1 1.5 1 1.5 1 .9 1.6 2.4 1.1 3 .8.1-.7.4-1.1.7-1.3-2.2-.3-4.5-1.1-4.5-5 0-1.1.4-2.1 1-2.8-.1-.3-.4-1.4.1-2.8 0 0 .8-.3 2.9 1.1a9.6 9.6 0 0 1 5.2 0c2-1.4 2.9-1.1 2.9-1.1.5 1.4.2 2.5.1 2.8.7.7 1 1.7 1 2.8 0 4-2.3 4.7-4.5 5 .4.4.8 1 .8 2.1v3.1c0 .3.2.6.7.5 4-1.4 6.9-5.2 6.9-9.7C22 6.6 17.5 2 12 2z"
            fill="currentColor"
          />
        </svg>
      </a>
      <a
        class="icon-link"
        href="https://twitter.com/yourname"
        aria-label="Twitter"
        title="Twitter"
      >
        <svg class="icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false">
          <path
            d="M4.5 4h4.4l3.4 4.7L16.7 4H20l-5.3 7.4L20.4 20h-4.4l-3.9-5.3L8.3 20H5l5.8-8.1L4.5 4z"
            fill="currentColor"
          />
        </svg>
      </a>
      <a
        class="icon-link"
        href="mailto:hello@example.com"
        aria-label="Email"
        title="Email"
      >
        <svg class="icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false">
          <path
            d="M4 6.5h16a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v8.5a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H4a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V8.5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2z"
            fill="currentColor"
          />
          <path
            d="M4.8 8.6 12 13.2l7.2-4.6"
            fill="none"
            stroke="var(--panel)"
            stroke-width="1.6"
            stroke-linecap="round"
            stroke-linejoin="round"
          />
        </svg>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="intro">
    这是一个开箱即用的极简双栏写作主题，基于 Astro 构建
    <br />注重可读性，内置浅色/深色及阅读模式，代码与样式结构清晰稳定
    <br />示例文章即完整用法指南，可快速搭建并轻松扩展
    <br />
    助你快速搭建并轻松维护一个简洁、专注的个人站点
  </div>

  <h2 class="section-title">当前关注</h2>
  <ul class="focus-list">
    <li>写作与内容结构</li>
    <li>Astro 主题与排版细节</li>
    <li>生活记录与长期主义</li>
  </ul>

  <h2 class="section-title">技术栈</h2>
  <div class="tech-stack">
    <section class="tech-group">
      <div class="tech-group-title">前端框架</div>
      <ul class="tech-list">
        <li class="tech-item">
          <div class="tech-item-head">
            <span class="tech-item-title">Astro / Vite</span>
          </div>
          <div class="tech-item-desc">内容站点与构建</div>
        </li>
        <li class="tech-item">
          <div class="tech-item-head">
            <span class="tech-item-title">CSS / 排版</span>
          </div>
          <div class="tech-item-desc">主题样式与排版细节</div>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </section>
    <section class="tech-group">
      <div class="tech-group-title">语言与工具</div>
      <ul class="tech-list">
        <li class="tech-item">
          <div class="tech-item-head">
            <span class="tech-item-title">TypeScript</span>
          </div>
          <div class="tech-item-desc">类型约束与脚本支持</div>
        </li>
        <li class="tech-item">
          <div class="tech-item-head">
            <span class="tech-item-title">Markdown</span>
          </div>
          <div class="tech-item-desc">内容写作与发布流程</div>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </section>
    
  </div>

  <h2 class="section-title">栏目指引</h2>
  <div class="site-guide">
    <article class="site-guide-item">
      <div class="site-guide-head">
        <h3 class="site-guide-title">归档</h3>
        <span class="site-guide-link">/archive/</span>
      </div>
      <p class="site-guide-desc">按年份分组的完整目录。</p>
    </article>
    <article class="site-guide-item">
      <div class="site-guide-head">
        <h3 class="site-guide-title">随笔</h3>
        <span class="site-guide-link">/essay/</span>
      </div>
      <p class="site-guide-desc">不成体系的碎片。</p>
    </article>
    <article class="site-guide-item">
      <div class="site-guide-head">
        <h3 class="site-guide-title">小记</h3>
        <span class="site-guide-link">/bits/</span>
      </div>
      <p class="site-guide-desc">朋友圈式短动态流，含一些自动化生成的草稿。</p>
    </article>
    <article class="site-guide-item">
      <div class="site-guide-head">
        <h3 class="site-guide-title">孩童</h3>
        <span class="site-guide-link">/kids/</span>
      </div>
      <p class="site-guide-desc">关于孩子成长时光笔记。</p>
    </article>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
